highlights.text: Cardi B has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “I Like It” is the highest at #9.
“I Wanna Know (feat. Bea Miller)” by NOTD and Bea Miller is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 70 spots at #85.
“One Dance” by Drake, WizKid, and Kyla has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 69 weeks straight.
“Let Me” by ZAYN is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #28.
